{"types":[{"section":"\n{{fr-noun|m}}\n\n# [[fate]], [[destiny]] {{gloss|consequences or effects predetermined by past events or a divine will}}\n#: {{uxi|fr|Je suis tombé amoureux de lui depuis le premier jour où je l'ai vu. C'était le '''sort.'''|t=I fell in love with him since the first day I laid eyes on him. It was '''destiny.'''}}\n# [[lot]] {{gloss|something used in determining a question by chance}}\n# [[spell]] {{gloss|magical incantation}}\n\n=====Usage notes=====\nAbstract nouns ''(a noun denoting an idea, quality, or state rather than a concrete object)'' in French [and other Romance languages] use definite articles prior to the noun—unlike English. I.e. C'était ''le'' '''''sort''''' qui nous a réunis = It was '''fate''' that brought us together.\n\n=====Derived terms=====\n{{col3|fr\n|coup du sort\n|faire un sort\n|ironie du sort\n|le sort en est jeté\n|mauvais sort\n|tirage au sort\n|tirer au sort}}\n\n=====Related terms=====\n* {{l|fr|sorcier}}\n* {{l|fr|sorte}}\n* {{l|fr|sortir}}\n\n","alt":[],"syn":[],"type":"noun","forms":[{"g":"m","n":"s"}],"html":"<p><span class=\"headword-line\"><strong class=\"Latn headword\" lang=\"fr\">sort</strong>&nbsp;<span class=\"gender\"><abbr title=\"masculine gender\">m</abbr></span> (<i>plural</i> <b class=\"Latn form-of lang-fr p-form-of\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/sorts#French\" title=\"sorts\">sorts</a></b>)</span>\n</p><ol><li><a href=\"/wiki/fate\" title=\"fate\">fate</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/destiny\" title=\"destiny\">destiny</a> <span class=\"mention-gloss-paren\">(</span><span class=\"mention-gloss\">consequences or effects predetermined by past events or a divine will</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-paren\">)</span>\n<dl><dd><span class=\"h-usage-example\"><i class=\"Latn mention e-example\" lang=\"fr\">Je suis tombé amoureux de lui depuis le premier jour où je l'ai vu. C'était le <b>sort.</b></i> ― <span class=\"e-translation\">I fell in love with him since the first day I laid eyes on him. It was <b>desti